graph TD
  subgraph Ingestion
    A[HTTP Endpoint] --> B[Request Parser]
    B --> C{Valid schema?}
    C -->|No| D[Return 400]
    C -->|Yes| E[Enqueue to Kafka]
  end

  subgraph Processing
    E --> F[Stream Processor]
    F --> G{Needs enrichment?}
    G -->|Yes| H[Enrich from Redis]
    G -->|No| I[Write to Postgres]
    H --> I
  end

  subgraph Notification
    I --> J{Alert condition?}
    J -->|Yes| K[Send to PagerDuty]
    J -->|No| L[Update dashboard]
  end

  D --> M([End])
  K --> M
  L --> M
